Defeat 5 designated monsters.
Open the backpack and heal yourself once with a Secondary Healing Potion.
Defeat monsters and collect some Crystallization Residues. Go into town to find the blacksmith and give him the materials.
Gather some Minerals to the blacksmith. Mineral can be found near the beach.
Talk to the blacksmith to open the equipment crafting interface and make a Stone Sword.
Open the Talent Tree interface, switch to Combat Specialization, and upgrade the Combat Mastery 1 node.
Gather some Ordinary Wood and give it to the mayor, and he will give you some props for farming.
